CERTIFICATE OF CONCURRENCE
This is to certify that Solar Star California XIX, LLC ("Solar Star XIX") assents to and concurs in the Rate Schedule described below which Kingbird Solar A, LLC has filed, and hereby files this Certificate of Concurrence in lieu of the filing of the Rate Schedule specified. Joint Rate Schedule: Shared Facilities Common Ownership Agreement among Kingbird Solar, LLC, AV Solar Ranch 1, LLC and Whirlwind Solar Star, LLC Designated Filing Company (DFC): Kingbird Solar A, LLC
DFC Tariff Program: Electric MBR

Dated: October 13, 2015
